'From Squeak3.1alpha of 28 February 2001 [latest update: #4284] on 23 August 2001 at 9:34:32 pm'!"Change Set:		RenameOnCR-arDate:			23 August 2001Author:			Andreas RaabAllow users to accept the name of a project on hitting enter."!!EToyProjectRenamerMorph methodsFor: '-- all --' stamp: 'ar 8/23/2001 21:33'!fieldForProjectName	| tm |	tm _ self genericTextFieldNamed: 'projectname'.	tm crAction: (MessageSend receiver: self selector: #doOK).	tm setBalloonText: 'Pick a name 24 characters or less and avoid the following characters: : < > | / \ ? * " .'.	^tm	! !